{"title":"麦收小景","authors":["孙隼"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":6,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦收小景（诗两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孙隼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉和镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"布谷鸟儿叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏收已来到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉急忙拿起镰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一怔，忽又放下了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉对镰瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰头窄又小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨洼多少磨镰石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收过千顷麦和稻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉对镰瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心喜脸上笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社成立第一年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"镰儿沙沙像飞刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉对镰瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜心蹦蹦跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社成立第二年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器代替笨镰刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老汉对镰瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握镰怀中抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心头思念共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏主席好领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦垛高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社麦场真红火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半天空里飘新歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子像在十重楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们如站九重阁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是楼，不是阁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶蓝天麦垛高。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}